OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780413074
OL,3,CNew seasonal route from Jersey to UK
OL,4,Ctakes flight
OL,6,FThe first direct and daily Loganair
OL,7,Fflight to East Midlands Airport took
OL,8,Foff from Jersey on Sunday 31 May.
OL,10,FIt's one of four new seasonal routes
OL,11,Favailable this summer, including
OL,12,FNorwich and Paris, with Bordeaux to
OL,13,Fcome.
OL,15,FThe Scottish airline took over several
OL,16,Flifeline services to the UK following
OL,17,Fthe collapse of Blue Islands last
OL,18,FNovember.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
