FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780413074
OL,3,CNew seasonal route from Jersey to UK
OL,4,Ctakes flight
OL,6,FIt's also the first time Loganair has
OL,7,Fflown to France in its history, with
OL,8,FSunday's morning flight to Paris.
OL,10,FThe Jersey to Norwich route launched
OL,11,Fearlier this month, with flights to
OL,12,FBordeaux starting next month.
OL,14,FOriginally Loganair had planned a new
OL,15,Froute to Dublin as part of this
OL,16,Fseasonal expansion, but due to demand
OL,17,Fthe airline says it was changed to
OL,18,FBordeaux.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
