OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780413074
OL,3,CNew seasonal route from Jersey to UK
OL,4,Ctakes flight
OL,6,FLoganair Chief Executive Luke
OL,7,FFarajallah said: "The way airlines
OL,8,Ftend to work is we talk to multiple
OL,9,Fairports at one time.
OL,11,F"We had reached agreement with Dublin,
OL,12,Fbut very quickly, hot on the heels of
OL,13,Fthat, we'd also had a very good offer
OL,14,Ffrom Bordeaux.
OL,16,F"As a consequence of that and because
OL,17,FDublin is already served from Jersey,
OL,18,Fwe made a decision to switch from
OL,19,FDublin to this new route."
OL,26,@oD@ROUsD@AOUxD@AOU
