OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780413074
OL,3,CNew seasonal route from Jersey to UK
OL,4,Ctakes flight
OL,6,FAll of the new routes will be operated
OL,7,Fby ATR-72 600 aircraft, with these
OL,8,Fschedules:
OL,10,FSaturdays from 9 May to 19 September
OL,11,Fand Wednesdays 3 June to 16 September
OL,12,F2026
OL,14,FDaily from 31 May to 24 October 2026.
OL,16,FTuesdays, Thursdays and Sundays from
OL,17,F31 May to 22 October 2026.
OL,19,FMondays and Fridays from 19 June to 5
OL,20,FOctober 2026.
